BootstrapAccordionBlockBundle
-----------------------------

Implements an AlphaLemon CMS app-block capable to manage a Twitter Bootstrap accordion
by a nice ajax powered inteface.

Installation
------------

You can add the **BootstrapAccordionBlockBundle Bundle** to your application adding it to your composer.json
file:

.. code-block:: text

    {
        "require": {
            "alphalemon/app-bootstrap-accordion-bundle": "1.0.*"
        }
    }

Unit test
---------

The bunde is fully unit tested.
